    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A Nahua constellation also known by two other Nahuatl terms, Yohualteuctli and Yacahuiztli. Scholars have argued for various identifications with known asterisms.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000320/GRI-FloCo</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
